name: skyup
additional_notices: The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: Skyup aims for a more accurate Defi ecosystem. Skyup has established its DEX platform, and convenient token swaps, staking, and liquidity registration are possible through the Skyup DE_FI platform. Skyup also aims to link main profiles between users to unique NFT repositories.
